snippet.title: Shadow Corridor - Announcement Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ http://nisamerica.com/shadow-corridor/

You are surrounded by darkness, and survival is the only option! Explore the mazes of barely-lit hallways set in Japanese locales to find helpful items and your way out. But tread carefully, as the spirits of the cursed Noh mask are smarter than you think.

Coming October 26, 2021!

#ShadowCorridor
